title: Limp Bizkit - Greatest Videoz [2005] DVD5
description: Limp Bizkit - Greatest Videoz [2005] DVD5 Limp Bizkit is an American rap rock band from Jacksonville, Florida. Their lineup consists of Fred Durst (lead vocals), Sam Rivers (bass, backing vocals), John Otto (drums, percussion), DJ Lethal (turntables), and Wes Borland (guitars, backing vocals). The band has been nominated for three Grammy Awards, have sold 40 million records worldwide and won several other awards Greatest Videoz is a DVD companion to the band's compilation album Greatest Hitz. The DVD compiles music videos from the band's albums Three Dollar Bill, Yall$, Significant Other, Chocolate Starfish and the Hot Dog Flavored Water, Results May Vary and The Unquestionable Truth (Part 1).
